page.title: 12BIRD-COUNT IN HARBOUR(cont)
page.content:
The gulls to be seen are the{Great}(3) &{Lesser}(3);{Black-backed;Herring}(4) {Common}(4); and{Black-headed}(4)
In Summer the {Tern}population arrives These include {Arctic}(3);{Common}(3); {Roseate}(2) & {Little Tern}(2).
After torrential rain {Kingfishers}(2) can be seen feeding from the moored yachts.
Pwllheli's {duck}population numbers eleven species.These include:{Mallard (3);{Teal}(3);{Wigeon}(3);{Shoveler } (3);{Shelduck}(3);{Tufted}(2);{Pochard (2);{Goldeneye}(2);{Red-breasted {Merganser}(2);{Scaup}(1);{Eider}(1).
